Description:Introducing our straightforward chat app – no frills, no fuss. Skip the hassle of signing up and logging in. With our app, it's all about simplicity. Just pick an avatar and a unique username, and you're in.

Powered by basic socket technology, our app enables real-time chatting. Connect with friends or new acquaintances instantly. Send text messages back and forth with ease.

Plus, registered users can delete their messages, giving you control over your conversations. It's all about keeping it simple and straightforward – the perfect choice for no-nonsense, basic chatting.



Technology Stack: React, ExpressJs, NodeJs, MongoDB, Socket
